data.description: Classic meets modern in this South Daytona retreat! Updated bathrooms, laminate floors, and modern appliances bring a fresh new feel to the space, timeless white cabinetry and a sunshine-friendly skylight keep this home effortlessly chic! Relax in style by the private screened saltwater pool adorned with retractable awnings and lush tropical foliage! The kitchen layout creates a seamless workflow and the large basin sink makes cleanup a breeze! A dedicated laundry room and privacy fence add to the luxury of this lovely abode! Situated near shopping, parks, restaurants, and schools - you won't want to miss out on this opportunity! Call today to schedule a showing!
